[SN]TITLE[SN]
Alltwen grass fire: Crews tackle Conwy mountain blaze

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Firefighters have been tackling a grassland fire on a Conwy county mountain.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Four crews were sent to the scene at Alltwen mountain, near Dwygyfylchi, on Saturday at 22:45 BST.
North Wales Fire Service said on Sunday morning the situation was under control.
Householders were advised to shut their windows and doors to avoid smoke coming in.
